"{\"uid\": \"thedailybeast.com-us-gold-medalist-maggie-steffens-reveals-shock-death-of-sister-in-law-at-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Breaking News Intern  Three-time Olympic gold medallist Maggie Steffens paid tribute to her late sister-in-law, Lulu Conner in anInstagram post, Saturday, revealing the 26-year-old had suddenly died in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 112, \"end\": 116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"score\": 0.9999723846162912, \"rank\": 2.761528993482533e-05, \"text\": \"Lulu\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\"}, {\"begin\": 202, \"end\": 207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999901222054, \"rank\": 9.877734675168935e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Conner died after traveling to theParis Olympicsto cheer on Steffens, suffering what the Olympic water polo player called a \\\"medical emergency,\\\" according to the Associated Press.\", \"from\": 210, \"to\": 389, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 372, \"end\": 388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.999999273604808, \"rank\": 7.263876241295066e-07, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No cause of death was provided.\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 421, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Conner was a fan of the entire U.S. water polo team, so much so that she made a water polo clock chain for fellow water polo booster, Flavor Flav, according to theAssociated Press.\", \"from\": 423, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Conner passed at the age of 26 on July 24, according to Steffens' post.\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 676, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was so excited for the Olympic Games,\\\" Steffens told the Associated Press through her tears.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 756, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.999999273604808, \"rank\": 7.263876241295066e-07, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She's the light of the world.\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She just brings so much joy to everyone.\\\"\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Saturday, Steffens posted three photos of her and Conner through the years.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first was a selfie of the two, the caption read: \\\"Wedding dress shopping in NYC just me and you, CAN'T WAIT TO BE SISTERS!\\\"\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by Maggie Steffens (@maggie.steffens)  Steffens and Bobby Conner, Lulu's older brother, were married last November in Puerto Rico.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maggie Steffens\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\"}, {\"begin\": 1139, \"end\": 1143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"score\": 0.9999723846162912, \"rank\": 2.761528993482533e-05, \"text\": \"Lulu\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\"}, {\"begin\": 1191, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.9999316221233304, \"rank\": 2.288391010194279e-05, \"text\": \"Puerto Rico\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Puerto_Rico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The second, a Polaroid of Conner and Steffens along with other women with a caption that read: \\\"Getting ready suite 11/11 in San Juan, OFFICIALLY SISTERS!\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1219, \"end\": 1227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instant_camera\", \"score\": 0.9999811760597398, \"rank\": 1.8780490657759752e-05, \"text\": \"Polaroid\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instant_camera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instant_camera\"}, {\"begin\": 1330, \"end\": 1338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Juan,_Puerto_Rico\", \"score\": 0.9678447264064957, \"rank\": 0.017339049115935777, \"text\": \"San Juan\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Juan,_Puerto_Rico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/San_Juan,_Puerto_Rico\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83e\\udd70\\\"  A post shared by Maggie Steffens (@maggie.steffens)  Finally, a photo of both the Conner and Steffens families standing together, with a caption that read: \\\"One big family of Steffens & Conners & more living like Lu \\ud83d\\ude4c\\ud83c\\udffc Super support team during this extremely difficult time.\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1382, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maggie Steffens\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\"}, {\"begin\": 1578, \"end\": 1580, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lutetium\", \"score\": 0.9711685480088623, \"rank\": 0.02240155983342921, \"text\": \"Lu\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lutetium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lutetium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\ud83d\\ude4f\\ud83c\\udffc\\u2764\\ufe0f\\\"  A post shared by Maggie Steffens (@maggie.steffens)  \\\"It's going to be a really hard couple weeks for all of us,\\\" Steffens told the Associated Press, adding that \\\"I am like so out of body in a way right now.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1669, \"end\": 1684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maggie Steffens\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\"}, {\"begin\": 1784, \"end\": 1800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.999999273604808, \"rank\": 7.263876241295066e-07, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I just keep trying to remind myself what Lulu would want and how she would be, you know, how can I embody her spirit the best.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1985, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And Lulu was somebody that she gave 150% to everything she did.\\\"\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And Lulu is here.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's here [in Paris],\\\" Steffens toldPeople.\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2115, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans gave an outpouring of condolences and well wishes in the comments to Steffens' post.\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2206, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Oh Mags sending hugs to you and Bobby.\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2247, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Heroes are remembered but legends never die and that smile of Lu's is legendary,\\\" one fan wrote.\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2344, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So sorry for your great loss.\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I lost a sister too so I know your pain.\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2417, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are thinking of you,\\\" another wrote.\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking News Intern  owen.lavine@thedailybeast.com  Got a tip?\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Send it to The Daily Beasthere.\", \"from\": 2523, \"to\": 2554, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ADVERTISEMENT  ADVERTISEMENT\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": []}]}"